@startwbs
* AgenticNativePlatform - Runtime Flow With Flux Operator And Static Cluster Roots
** 1. Flux control plane
*** Flux Operator
**** manages Flux controller lifecycle
*** FluxInstance/flux
**** sync.kind = GitRepository
**** sync.path = ./clusters/<topology>-<env>
*** GitRepository/platform
**** reads remote Git branch
*** Staged Kustomizations
**** platform-infrastructure
**** platform-secrets
**** platform-applications

** 2. North-south traffic path
*** External client
**** sends HTTP /v1 and /mcp
*** kgateway public-gateway
**** north-south entry point
**** routes traffic to agentgateway-proxy
*** agentgateway-proxy
**** protocol-aware AI gateway
**** /v1 -> litellm-upstream backend
**** /mcp -> kagent-tools-mcp-backend
*** LiteLLM
**** remote provider default path
**** optional external LM Studio path
**** optional in-cluster runtime path
*** agentregistry-inventory
**** internal control-plane catalog
**** default access via port-forward
**** not on the default public gateway path
*** MCP Governance dashboard
**** internal-only access via port-forward
**** backed by mcp-governance controller scans

** 3. Cluster components
*** platform plumbing
**** namespaces from apps/platform
**** cluster wrappers from clusters/<topology>-<env>
*** kgateway-system
**** kgateway controller
**** public-gateway
*** agentgateway-system
**** agentgateway controller
**** agentgateway-proxy
**** AgentgatewayBackend resources
**** AgentgatewayPolicy
*** kagent
**** kagent-controller
**** kagent-ui
**** kagent-tools
**** k8s-agent
**** kgateway-agent
**** istio-agent
**** promql-agent
**** observability-agent
**** argo-rollouts-agent
**** helm-agent
**** cilium-policy-agent
**** cilium-manager-agent
**** cilium-debug-agent
**** team-lead-agent-assist
**** grafana-mcp
**** Agent: k8s-a2a-agent
**** RemoteMCPServer: kagent-tool-server
*** ai-gateway
**** LiteLLM
*** ai-models
**** tei-embeddings
**** KServe control plane
**** optional Ollama or vLLM path
*** context
**** Qdrant
**** PostgreSQL
**** Redis
*** agentregistry
**** agentregistry-inventory
**** DiscoveryConfig/local
*** mcp-governance-system
**** mcp-governance-controller
**** mcp-governance-dashboard
**** MCPGovernancePolicy
**** GovernanceEvaluation
*** observability
**** Prometheus
**** Grafana
**** Loki
**** OpenTelemetry Collector
**** Phoenix
**** Tempo

** 4. Request and data paths
*** UI and agent path
**** kagent-ui -> kagent-controller
**** k8s-a2a-agent -> kagent-controller
**** k8s-agent -> kagent-controller
**** kgateway-agent -> kagent-controller
**** istio-agent -> kagent-controller
**** promql-agent -> kagent-controller
**** observability-agent -> kagent-controller
**** argo-rollouts-agent -> kagent-controller
**** helm-agent -> kagent-controller
**** cilium-policy-agent -> kagent-controller
**** cilium-manager-agent -> kagent-controller
**** cilium-debug-agent -> kagent-controller
**** team-lead-agent-assist -> kagent-controller
**** kagent-controller -> agentgateway /v1
*** MCP path
**** RemoteMCPServer -> agentgateway /mcp/kagent-tools
**** agentgateway -> kagent-tools backend
**** observability-agent -> grafana-mcp tool server
*** LLM path
**** agentgateway -> LiteLLM
**** LiteLLM -> Gemini / OpenAI / Anthropic / Bedrock / Vertex / others
**** LiteLLM -> optional LM Studio endpoint
**** LiteLLM -> optional Ollama or vLLM path
*** Context path
**** kagent-controller -> tei-embeddings
**** kagent-controller -> Qdrant
**** kagent-controller -> PostgreSQL
**** kagent-controller -> Redis
*** Inventory path
**** agentregistry-inventory -> catalogs kagent Agents
**** agentregistry-inventory -> catalogs MCPServer and RemoteMCPServer
**** operator -> port-forward -> inventory UI and public catalog API
*** Governance path
**** mcp-governance-controller -> scans agentgateway, kagent, and agentregistry resources
**** GovernanceEvaluation -> policyRef -> MCPGovernancePolicy
**** operator -> port-forward -> mcpg dashboard
*** Observability path
**** kagent-controller -> OpenTelemetry Collector
**** kagent-tools -> OpenTelemetry Collector
**** grafana-mcp -> Grafana API
**** grafana-mcp -> OpenTelemetry Collector
**** Prometheus -> grafana-mcp /metrics via ServiceMonitor
**** OpenTelemetry Collector -> Phoenix and Tempo
**** Prometheus, Tempo, and Loki -> Grafana
